{"id":1663,"date":"2024-08-23T21:09:16","date_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:09:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1663"},"modified":"2024-08-23T21:09:16","modified_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:09:16","slug":"absolite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/absolite\/","title":{"rendered":"Absolite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Absolite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Given to you by the trainer on the west side of Crystal Peak 1F after defeating her in battle. Requires Surf to reach.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Absol<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Crystal Peak<\/li>\n<li>Defeat the Elite 4 to access the crystal switches<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm06-rock-smash\/\">Rock Smash<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Defeat all the other trainers in Crystal Peak<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Enter Crystal Peak and follow the linear path going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/01-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-forward-in-crystal-peak.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path forward in Crystal Peak. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path forward in Crystal Peak.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Smash the breakable rocks blocking your path and use the ladder behind them to go deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/02-pokemon-unbound-using-the-ladder-to-go-down.jpg\" alt=\"Using the ladder to go down. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using the ladder to go down.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Surf to continue going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/03-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-forward.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue forward. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to continue forward.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn north to reach the area with interactable crystals.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/04-pokemon-unbound-surfing-toward-the-area-with-interactable-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Disable the <strong>red crystals<\/strong> and make sure the yellow and blue crystals are enabled.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/05-pokemon-unbound-disabling-the-red-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Disabling the red crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Disabling the red crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With the interactable crystal part done, backtrack to the east ladder and go to the higher level.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/06-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-ladder-to-the-upper-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the ladder to the upper floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the ladder to the upper floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Rock Climb to scale the wall to your south before following the path west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/07-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-go-down-then-following-the-path-west.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to go down, then following the path west. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Rock Climb to go down, then following the path west.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn south to continue on the path at the very western side (against a wall) and just follow this path downwards.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/08-pokemon-unbound-turning-south-and-continuing-on-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Turning south and continuing on the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Turning south and continuing on the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll soon see another button you can interact with to disable the blue crystals.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/09-pokemon-unbound-disabling-the-blue-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Disabling the blue crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Disabling the blue crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Backtrack to the scalable wall and climb up the yellow Rock Climb spot.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/10-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-scale-the-west-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to scale the west wall. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Rock Climb to scale the west wall.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the passageway over to the left-hand side \u2013 this leads to a different part of the cave at the end of the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/11-pokemon-unbound-walking-through-the-passageway-leading-to-a-different-area.jpg\" alt=\"Walking through the passageway leading to a different area. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking through the passageway leading to a different area.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once inside, go to the left and use Surf to follow the path west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/12-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-on-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue on the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to continue on the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Interact with the trainer at the end of the path and she\u2019ll challenge you to a battle as long as you\u2019ve defeated every other trainer on Crystal Peak.<\/p>\n<p>Defeating Mega Trainer Krystal rewards you with the Absolite.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/13-pokemon-unbound-approaching-mega-trainer-krystal.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching Mega Trainer Krystal. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching Mega Trainer Krystal.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table left\" style=\"min-width:860px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"6\" class=\"text-large\">Mega Trainer Krystal<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/14-pokemon-unbound-mega-trainer-krystal.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:60px;\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/15-pokemon-unbound-oranguru.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/16-pokemon-unbound-jellicent.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/17-pokemon-unbound-snorlax.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/18-pokemon-unbound-druddigon.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/absolite\/19-pokemon-unbound-mega-absol.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Pok\u00e9mon<\/th>\n<td>Oranguru<\/td>\n<td>Jellicent<\/td>\n<td>Snorlax<\/td>\n<td>Druddigon<\/td>\n<td>Mega Absol<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Normal\/Psychic<\/td>\n<td>Water\/Ghost<\/td>\n<td>Normal<\/td>\n<td>Dragon<\/td>\n<td>Dark\/Fairy<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ability<\/th>\n<td>Inner Focus<\/td>\n<td>Water Absorb<\/td>\n<td>Thick Fat<\/td>\n<td>Sheer Force<\/td>\n<td>Justified &#8211; Magic Bounce<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Held Item<\/th>\n<td>Light Clay<\/td>\n<td>Leftovers<\/td>\n<td>Choice Band<\/td>\n<td>Life Orb<\/td>\n<td>Absolite<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weaknesses<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dark (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ghost (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Grass (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Electric (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dark (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ice (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dragon (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Poison (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Steel (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Moves<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Psychic<\/li>\n<li>Reflect<\/li>\n<li>Light Screen<\/li>\n<li>Trick Room<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Hex<\/li>\n<li>Will-O-Wisp<\/li>\n<li>Strength Sap<\/li>\n<li>Trick Room<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Double-Edge<\/li>\n<li>Darkest Lariat<\/li>\n<li>Earthquake<\/li>\n<li>Fire Punch<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Outrage<\/li>\n<li>Sucker Punch<\/li>\n<li>Fire Punch<\/li>\n<li>Iron Tail<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Knock Off<\/li>\n<li>Play Rough<\/li>\n<li>Sucker Punch<\/li>\n<li>Swords Dance<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <pi